# Etsy Sales Manager — Cursor Rules
# Last updated: 2026-05-24 (ADR-017/018 reconciliation)
# These rules tell Cursor exactly where to look and what to follow for every domain.
# When in doubt: read the ADR first, then implement.

---

## Project Overview

This is **Etsy Sales Manager** — a Next.js 16 (App Router) + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + SQLite app
for managing an Etsy vintage/antique business (Trudy's Classic Treasures). It connects to Etsy via
OAuth, manages inventory, customers, orders, and generates reports and listing content (including
AI-assisted). It is a single-user local app.

Stack: Next.js 16, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, SQLite (via better-sqlite3 or equivalent), Node 20 LTS.

