- Picture storage and thumbnails (ADR-026): file validation, Sharp processing, canonical paths
- Report edge cases (ADR-013): empty data handling, PDF failure response, date filtering
- All 9 report endpoints (PDF + CSV) with date parameters
- AI settings API with masked values and connection test
- Global API error model + structured logging
- Migration system + seed data

